<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="../assets/xml/rss.xsl" media="all"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>写程序的龙龙 (Posts about redis)</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/</link><description></description><atom:link href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/categories/redis.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 03 Feb 2018 09:52:29 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>Nikola (getnikola.com)</generator><docs>http://blogs.law.harvard.edu/tech/rss</docs><item><title>测试时，Docker终端无法显示中文</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ce-shi-shi-dockerzhong-duan-wu-fa-xian-shi-zhong-wen/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;测试代码的时候，无法用print在Docker终端输出中文，对于这个问题，我们采用的办法是将要输出的信息记录在redis里，然后在主系统通过redis图形客户端查看，这样的好处在于:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol class="arabic simple"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;不需要改动docker镜像本身；&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;redis可以很好地支持中文；&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;测试过程可记录，容易追溯问题所在。&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>Docker</category><category>redis</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/ce-shi-shi-dockerzhong-duan-wu-fa-xian-shi-zhong-wen/</guid><pubDate>Sat, 30 Dec 2017 16:00:02 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>Redis修改默认端口</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/redisxiu-gai-mo-ren-duan-kou/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;pre class="literal-block"&gt;
&amp;gt;&amp;gt; emacs /etc/redis/redis.conf
port 8083
bind 0.0.0.0
&amp;gt;&amp;gt; redis-server /etc/redis/redis.conf
&lt;/pre&gt;</description><category>redis</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/redisxiu-gai-mo-ren-duan-kou/</guid><pubDate>Sat, 30 Dec 2017 15:31:05 GMT</pubDate></item></channel></rss>